<h2> What is a story you would love to hear about? </h2> <br>

<h5>*Hint* Think of funny or significant memories from your own life that you don't know about your friends and family.  No punctuation needed. All prompts will be pre-empted by "Write about.." so phrase accordingly.</h5>

<%= simple_form_for @prompt, html: { class: 'form-horizontal' } do |form| %><br>
	 <%= form.input :name, label: "New prompt:", as: :text %><br>
	 <%= form.association :category, label: "Select a category", label_method: :name %><br>
	 <%= form.button :submit, class: 'btn btn-default' %>
	  <% end %>